name: UNIX_BITS
doc:
Permissions, broken down by who they affect
where applicable, and what right they grant.

     [
         ['owner', 'read'],
         ['owner', 'write'],
         ['owner', 'execute'],
         ['group', 'read'],
         ['group', 'write'],
         ['group', 'execute'],
         ['other', 'read'],
         ['other', 'write'],
         ['other', 'execute'],
         ['setUid', undefined],
         ['setGid', undefined],
         ['sticky', undefined],
     ]
